{"tid":210113,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無對器官捐贈失望？","createTime":"2017-04-20T16:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T10:53:09.000Z","uid":12618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcfc75758f3dbad824c438d6e6c78e6c3977df05","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"上年中大朗朗心臟衰竭要換心<br />\n到有屍心換左 病情反覆最後都走左<br />\n<br />\n到而家鄧媽媽肝有事要換肝<br />\n鄭小姐出黎捐個活肝出黎比鄧媽媽<br />\n但鄧媽媽血管分支問題需要第二個肝再換<br />\n<br />\n唔係話challenge啲乜<br />\n經過呢兩件事大家有無對器官捐贈改觀/失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw器官捐贈既成功例子有好多既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申上網填器官捐贈</span>"},{"pid":"69f8129e4f4c648edc127245cb768b4aa7168da8","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb30323105c198a31af9ac77a370f64bd38b00a","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b92b9ebf3e8d60f0618315123539866d06aba3","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d2d05373db85fe07873266a7c34a97b1a42db2","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb7b320ca15408a757f7186891b92baf4dc28c3","tid":210113,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e13634ba8db7138e5b0d68c8d40d8ce191346c","tid":210113,"uid":38797,"like":0,"